^https:\/\/acs\.m\.taobao\.com\/gw\/mtop\.alibaba\.advertisementservice\.getadv reject-dict
^https:\/\/acs\.m\.taobao\.com\/gw\/mtop\.alimama\.etao\.config\.query\/.+?etao_advertise reject-dict
